{"tid":868201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發奇想]用抖音宣傳港獨有冇可能","createTime":"2018-10-19T09:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T14:40:22.000Z","uid":211412,"like":57,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3028df3ea00d0cfa45456950d45fbcc336cb348a","tid":868201,"uid":211412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"我知道一定會被Ban<br />\n但係只要不斷開分身AC upload相關嘅片<br />\n應該點都可以影響到少部分人嘅睇法<br />\n再唔係累到抖音收皮都唔錯<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191eb8b064b3fdc87dacefb1a83e71bc5d6e1dfb","tid":868201,"uid":33481,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"係娛樂地方搞呢d 死多兩錢重"},{"pid":"817ff45667fd3c01ce1cdb3faefef0ebf345ea31","tid":868201,"uid":66260,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"你post任何野佢地會審查<br />\n你條片出街後幾秒就會被刪<br />\n冇人會睇到"},{"pid":"c515a21c70d4f19974164a579c295da35c9dfabb","tid":868201,"uid":25797,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:41:08.000Z","msg":"on9仔 你唔撚好話去天安門宣揚港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f32ebc8eb51810a82521490d86775848163e510","tid":868201,"uid":550,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:41:14.000Z","msg":"我們一起去港獨<br />\n一起屌鳩習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcb1260d1c6ba57bea182f1cd592fcafab9f769","tid":868201,"uid":35152,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:41:45.000Z","msg":"得罪講句  <br />\n用抖音既都係on9<br />\n你同啲on9宣傳港獨有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb57629480565eed939e0c272814efc7f5156c5","tid":868201,"uid":12468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:43:27.000Z","msg":"反效果就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef72a55a2a2a8a01ff7c43fd2e93b8f9245e7577","tid":868201,"uid":109462,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:48:43.000Z","msg":"一、要娛樂化。抖音畢竟主要用於娛樂，內容太正經根本無人會睇，所以要將政治訊息娛樂化，例如改編一首歌或者設計一個小品橋段，內容可以係保衛粵語、屌共產黨等等。<br />\n<br />\n二、要反共不反華。抖音主要觀眾群都係大陸人、或者文化上親近大陸，既反共又反華只會引起觀眾憤怒，亦唔符合逆向統戰大陸民眾嘅原始動機。因此唔可以有針對中國人民族嘅內容，要集中火力打共產黨。<br />\n<br />\n三、要有遊擊戰準備。內容、戶口可能隨時被封禁，要有打網上遊擊戰嘅心理準備，呢頭被滅聲，另一邊就要再有新內容。"},{"pid":"e62bc6f191acbe39c4283456b855f04619d8faec","tid":868201,"uid":70060,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbf54432afff3018a6fe7e5189baec9514d42bc1","tid":868201,"uid":182499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:56:40.000Z","msg":"宣傳港獨畀你用埋youtube都冇用啦 重話用抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24cc7d153648845d15ce4bc7d6b28012fda6a0b","tid":868201,"uid":181294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:48:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d62f0a333c20fbd3ecb839ee47eeb09be1bbd8cf","tid":868201,"uid":5995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:50:58.000Z","msg":"港獨手勢舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5a79f3d70a14c2532b8bd62789fccc47d632ea","tid":868201,"uid":191762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"其實乜嘢係抖音？"},{"pid":"4428fd226aa0c5c3f9e0caee02cf9026f6d73977","tid":868201,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"會唔會未廣傳就被刪，吃力不討好？"},{"pid":"00ffee2a09b39f5dc53c4f7db8a2357f1823e2d3","tid":868201,"uid":55375,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"dfcb1260d1c6ba57bea182f1cd592fcafab9f769","tid":868201,"uid":35152,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:41:45.000Z","msg":"得罪講句  <br />\n用抖音既都係on9<br />\n你同啲on9宣傳港獨有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/n